<Content>I bought this for my brother as a Christmas gift.  A few days later I decided to try it out and was pretty dissapointed.  It was pretty flimsy, as the plastic material felt thin and weak.  The headphone input was also messed up.  It would only send sound to one ear piece unless you wiggled it around.  Needless to say I quickly returned it.  I don't know if I got unlucky and bought a defective player, but it was a piece of junk.  I was pretty dissapointed as I have other Rio products that are much more durable.  
