<Review ID>5393840
<Product Name>Rio One 64 MB MP3 Player
<Title>Adequate
<Date>Mon Jan 13 00:00:00 CST 2003
<Content>The Rio One is a nice little MP3 player. Very compact. Good sound. Easy to use. It would be ideal as a &quot;beginner&quot; unit. The battery flap is easily knocked open, making the battery fall out. The music is still stored but what a pain. Also, since it only has one battery, it is used up VERY quickly and there is not an AC adapter option. Finally, the unit sometimes does not operate at all. I cannot figure out why but the problem, thus far, always goes away. Spend a bit more on a better unit, it'll be worth it.  
<Overall>2

